sellerCard.description: I'm Minahil, a certified Web Developer with over 3+ years of experience. I've experienced WordPress, Wix, Squarespace, Shopify, etc. CMS platforms, HTML, CSS, PHP, Javascript, and any issues regarding WordPress websites. I've developed 200+ websites in the last seven years. I also have a skilled and experienced team for doing all kinds of websites. Client satisfaction is my main goal. So I always prioritize all my client's requirements and give my best effort to achieve their success. Send me a message if you have any questions.

description.content:
Are you looking to get a responsive WordPress Website Design or do you want to redesign web-site to make it professional & mobile responsive?


Why Me?


I am a WordPress Developer and into website development for more than 7 years having experience in building different type of Web-sites including but not limited to Blog, Ecommerce Website, Digital Agency, Marketing Agency, Consultancy and Business, Job Portal, Real Estate, Beauty Niche, Handyman Services, Trucking, Notary and many more. 



What You Will Get:


  • Highly Professional WordPress Design
  • E-commerce and payment gateways integration
  • Custom WordPress web-site
  • WordPress customization
  • Build Landing page
  • Wordpress Elementor
  • Ecommerce web-site
  • Convert Adobe XD, Wix, PSD, Webflow, Figma to WordPress
  • Modern website using DIVI, Elementor
  • PREMIUM Theme & Plugins
  • Mobile Friendly Design
  • Image Slider & Parallax effect
  • Security, SEO and Speed Optimization
  • Google Map & Analytics
  • Mailchimp and Subscription form
  • Popups & Call to actions
  • SSL & Payment Integration
  • Social media & Contact form


Why Me:


  • 100% Satisfaction 
  • Fast delivery
  • Free support after order delivery
  • Unlimited revision


If you have any questions then please contact me!

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am ready to buy! What do I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: A domain(example.com) and a hosting account (if you don't have these I will assist you).I will also need your logo (optional), names & no. of pages, a few sentences about your website/company, e mail address to configure form, a few images (I will try to arrange similar ones).

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you work alone or in a team?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have a team of creative developers. We can manage any number of projects without any problem

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my site be seo optimized?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we will optimize your website for seo using yoast plugin.The basic seo structure will be provide in all packages.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my site be responsiveness on all mobile and tablet devices?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, your website will be 100% responsive on all devices.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do we offer WordPress Management Services?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! We offer WordPress Management Services. This includes timely updating your plugins, theme & WordPress and also it includes creating timely backups of the website. You can contact us for WordPress Management Services.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if your requirements does not meet any of my package?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Don't worry, just contacts me and we will discuss your requirements and we will make a deal according to your requirements.
